The paper focuses on the development of efficient deep neural networks for on-device edge scenarios, which is a common theme in the computer science sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SY). Given that the paper specifically deals with the generation of efficient neural networks through generative synthesis, it is most likely to be classified under cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.SY.
